longBusinessSummary: Onano Industrial Corp. provides slimmed opto-electronic glass and alloy materials in Taiwan. The company offers slimming, polishing, and film coating services for TFT-LCD, OLED, solar cell glass, etc. Its products are used in various applications, including smart phones, tablets, ultra-thin laptops, and others. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Taoyuan City, Taiwan.
